	MythicTooltips: {
		Base: -{0} Signature Weapon-
		Argus: Argus'
		Your: Your
		Draedon: Draedon's
		Solyn: Solyn's
		Anahita: Anahita's
		Amidias: Amidias'
		CalClone: Shadow of Calamitas'
		Cultist: The Lunatic Cultist's
		ND: The Deity's
		Mars: Mars'
		EoL: The Empress of Light's
